'''[[也门|也门]]'''派代表团参加了9月15日至10月1日在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[悉尼|悉尼]]举行的'''[[2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]'''。此次参赛是也门第三次以统一国家的身份参加[[夏季奥林匹克运动会|夏季奥林匹克运动会]]。也门代表团派出了两名[[田赛和径赛|田径]]运动员：{{tsl|en|Basheer Al-Khewani|贝希尔·赫瓦尼}}和{{tsl|en|Hana Ali Saleh|哈娜·阿里·萨利赫}}，二人在各自参赛项目的首轮比赛中均未晋级。

==背景==
1981年1月1日，[[也门奥委会|也门奥委会]]得到[[国际奥委会|国际奥委会]]的承认<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/yemen|title=Yemen – National Olympic Committee (NOC)|publisher=[[國際奧林匹克委員會|International Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025031305/https://www.olympic.org/yemen|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。20世纪80年代，[[北也门|北也门]]和[[南也门|南也门]]都曾在奥运会上亮相<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YMD/|title=South Yemen|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021151601/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YMD/|archive-date=2018-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YAR/|title=North Yemen|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021151319/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YAR/|archive-date=2018-10-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。1990年[[也门统一|也门统一]]后<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-14704951|title=Yemen profile – Timeline – BBC News|publisher=[[BBC|BBC Online]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180910191911/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-14704951|archive-date=2018-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该国参加了[[1992年夏季奥运会|1992年夏季奥运会]]后的每届奥运会<ref name="YEMSR">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YEM/|title=Yemen|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417092259/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YEM/|archive-date=2020-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。本届奥运会是也门统一后第三次参加奥运会，而也门还未曾参加过[[冬奥会|冬奥会]]<ref name="YEMSR" />。2000年夏季奥运会于2000年9月15日至10月1日举行；共有10651名运动员代表199支[[国家奥林匹克委员会|国家奥委会]]参赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/sydney-2000|title=Sydney 2000 Summer Olympics – results & video highlights|publisher=International Olympic Committee|accessdate=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703164903/https://www.olympic.org/sydney-2000|archive-date=2018-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。也门派出了两名田径选手{{tsl|en|Basheer Al-Khewani|贝希尔·赫瓦尼}}和{{tsl|en|Hana Ali Saleh|哈娜·阿里·萨利赫}}参加悉尼奥运会<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YEM/summer/2000/|title=Yemen at the 2000 Sydney Summer Games|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025031306/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/YEM/summer/2000/|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，赫瓦尼担任开幕式旗手<ref name="YEMSR" />。

==田径==
{{main article|2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会田径比赛}}

贝希尔·赫瓦尼在参加悉尼奥运会时年仅18岁，这也是他唯一一次参加奥运会<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/al/basheer-al-khewani-1.html|title=Basheer Al-Khewani Bio, Stats, and Results|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418004618/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/al/basheer-al-khewani-1.html|archive-date=2020-04-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/basheer-al-khewani|title=Basheer AL KHEWANI – Olympic Athletics – Yemen|publisher=[[International_Olympic_Committee|International Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025070928/https://www.olympic.org/basheer-al-khewani|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月22日，他参加了{{tsl|en|Athletics at the 2000 Summer Olympics – Men's 400 metres|2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会田径比赛－男子400米|男子400米}}首轮比赛，并分在第八组。他以49.72秒的成绩完赛，在同组选手中排名最后一位被淘汰<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/ATH/mens-400-metres-round-one.html|title=Athletics at the 2000 Sydney Summer Games: Men's 400 metres Round One|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417115251/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/ATH/mens-400-metres-round-one.html|archive-date=2020-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。赫瓦尼的成绩比冠军得主{{tsl|en|United States at the 2000 Summer Olympics|2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会美国代表团|美国}}选手[[麥可·詹森_(田徑運動員)|迈克尔·约翰逊]]的决赛成绩43.84秒慢了6.32秒<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/ATH/mens-400-metres.html|title=Athletics at the 2000 Sydney Summer Games: Men's 400 metres|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417171557/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/ATH/mens-400-metres.html|archive-date=2020-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/sydney-2000/athletics/400m-men|title=Sydney 2000 400m men – Olympic Sydney 2000 Athletics|publisher=[[International_Olympic_Committee|International Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327060208/https://www.olympic.org/sydney-2000/athletics/400m-men|archive-date=2017-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

哈娜·阿里·萨利赫在参加奥运会时32岁，这同样也是她唯一一次参加奥运会<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/sa/hana-ali-saleh-1.html|title=Hana Ali Saleh Bio, Stats, and Results|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418004623/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/sa/hana-ali-saleh-1.html|archive-date=2020-04-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/hana-ali-saleh|title=Hana Ali SALEH – Olympic Athletics – Yemen|publisher=[[International_Olympic_Committee|International Olympic Committee]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025031325/https://www.olympic.org/hana-ali-saleh|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她是首位代表也门参加奥运会的女性选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nationalyemen.com/2012/07/22/yemeni-athletes-travel-to-london-for-2012-olympic-games/|title=Yemeni athletes travel to London for 2012 Olympic Games|publisher=National Yemen Newspaper|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025070920/https://nationalyemen.com/2012/07/22/yemeni-athletes-travel-to-london-for-2012-olympic-games/|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。9月27日，她参加了{{tsl|en|Athletics at the 2000 Summer Olympics – Women's 200 metres|2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会田径比赛－女子200米|女子200米}}首轮比赛，并分在第二组。结果她以30.36秒的成绩完赛，同样排名小组最后一位被淘汰<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/ATH/womens-200-metres-round-one.html|title=Athletics at the 2000 Sydney Summer Games: Women's 200 metres Round One|publisher=Sports Reference|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417105047/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2000/ATH/womens-200-metres-round-one.html|archive-date=2020-04-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。萨利赫的成绩比同组第七名慢了6秒多，比金牌得主{{tsl|en|Bahamas at the 2000 Summer Olympics|2000年夏季奥林匹克运动会巴哈马代表团|巴哈马}}选手[[保利娜·戴维斯-汤普森|保利娜·戴维斯-汤普森]]的决赛成绩22.27秒则慢了8.09秒<ref name="200mwomenfinal">{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/sydney-2000/athletics/200m-women|title=Sydney 2000 200m women – Olympic Sydney 2000 Athletics|publisher=International Olympic Committee|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327061100/https://www.olympic.org/sydney-2000/athletics/200m-women|archive-date=2017-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{notetag|女子200米原金牌得主是决赛中跑出21.84秒的美国选手[[马里恩·琼斯|马里恩·琼斯]]。然而，琼斯在2007年承认了[[體育禁藥|违反兴奋剂规定]]，并于12月被剥夺奖牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/dec/12/usa.athletics|title=Athlete Jones stripped of Olympic medals|last=Bridge|first=Sarah|date=2007-12-12|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025070905/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/dec/12/usa.athletics|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。原本获得银牌的汤普森于2010年6月递补获得金牌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/olympics/trackandfield/news/story?id=5277604|title=Pauline Davis-Thompson receives Olympic gold medal stripped from Marion Jones|date=2010-06-11|publisher=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|accessdate=2018-10-24|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025071040/http://www.espn.com/olympics/trackandfield/news/story?id=5277604|archive-date=2018-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。如果琼斯的成绩有效，则萨利赫与琼斯决赛成绩的差距为8.52秒<ref name="200mwomenfinal"/>。}}。

